677
00:50:43,200 --> 00:50:45,964
Yeah, fellows. I sold the cow
for some magic beans !

678
00:50:46,036 --> 00:50:50,370
Beans !
[ Squawking ]

679
00:50:50,441 --> 00:50:52,466
[ Mickey ] But Donald!

680
00:50:52,543 --> 00:50:56,138
These are not ordinary beans!
They're magic beans!

681
00:50:56,213 --> 00:51:00,149
If you plant these beans
in the light of a full moon,
do you know what'll happen ?

682
00:51:00,217 --> 00:51:03,380
Yes ! We get more beans !
[ Squawking ]

683
00:51:03,454 --> 00:51:07,515
- No, no, Donald !
- [ Donald ] Magic beans! Phooey!

684
00:51:08,792 --> 00:51:10,726
[ Bergen ] Poor Mickey,

685
00:51:10,794 --> 00:51:13,820
cheated into trading his cow
for a handful of beans.

686
00:51:13,897 --> 00:51:16,627
Tsk, tsk, tsk.
What a mean trick!

687
00:51:16,700 --> 00:51:20,033
Swindling an innocent farmer
out of all he owned...

688
00:51:20,104 --> 00:51:23,870
and lying to him, telling him
that the beans were magic.

689
00:51:25,008 --> 00:51:27,875
Planted in the light
of a full moon!

690
00:51:27,945 --> 00:51:31,472
What a shame to deceive
a simple little peasant.

691
00:51:31,548 --> 00:51:33,982
Magic beans, indeed!

692
00:51:34,051 --> 00:51:36,611
- Light of a full moon.
-[ Charlie ] Bergen ? Oh, Bergen!

693
00:51:36,687 --> 00:51:39,178
-[ Bergen ] What ?
-[ Luana ] There's something moving.

694
00:51:39,256 --> 00:51:43,386
[ Bergen ] Why,yes. Well, maybe
there is some magic in them !

695
00:51:43,460 --> 00:51:46,520
All right, now let's all keep quiet
and see what happens.

696
00:52:02,120 --> 00:52:05,317
[ Snoring ]

697
00:52:15,367 --> 00:52:18,302
[ Snoring ]

698
00:52:24,876 --> 00:52:26,810
Mmm.

699
00:52:33,919 --> 00:52:35,853
[ Giggles ]

700
00:54:00,539 --> 00:54:03,406
[ Bergen ] And all
through the night, it grew,

701
00:54:03,475 --> 00:54:05,568
onward and upward.

702
00:54:05,644 --> 00:54:08,442
[ Charlie ] That thing
is a menace to aviation.

703
00:54:10,749 --> 00:54:12,683
[ Bergen ] And so,
with the coming of dawn,

704
00:54:12,751 --> 00:54:16,118
we find the bewildered farmers
staring at a mammoth castle,

705
00:54:16,188 --> 00:54:18,122
